    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税引发避险需求，金价涨至接近纪录高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收关税，并威胁对欧盟采取同样的措施后，黄金价格在避险资产热潮中上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加征关税后，交易员纷纷抛售风险资产，以太币和 Memecoins 暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/crypto-bears-brunt-of-risk-off-moves-after-trump-unveils-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普对美国主要贸易伙伴征收关税的举措引发了加密货币的抛售，小型代币指数有望创下近三年来最大幅度的两日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/crypto-bears-brunt-of-risk-off-moves-after-trump-unveils-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:20:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甚至在唐纳德·特朗普总统于周六宣布对美国进口产品征收大范围关税之前​​，人们对他将采取何种措施的猜测就已推动黄金价格创下自 3 月份以来的最大月度涨幅。与此同时，页岩油气开采活动也显示出放缓的迹象。尽管全球能源转型投资超过 2 万亿美元，但针对气候相关公司的融资交易却在减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大石油因低于预期的 10% 关税而感到欣慰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/canadian-energy-dodges-cataclysm-with-lower-tariffs-gulf-outlet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令降低原油关税，并可能让生产商完全避免对部分原油征收关税，加拿大的能源行业可能暂时躲过了与美国贸易战的灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/canadian-energy-dodges-cataclysm-with-lower-tariffs-gulf-outlet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 21:55:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
